name: Mission Demolition (Wesley Chun)
description:
Mission Demolition is an Angry Birds clone made in Unity with C#. This project is for MI 231 at Michigan State University, taught by Jeremy Bond. 

Fire away at various castles by pulling back on the slingshot. 

Use the Switch View button to change views of the slingshot, castle, and whole view.

(Unfortunately, after the 2nd level, the game breaks)
